    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
}</code></pre>

                                                <p class="mb-3">The <code>place-items</code> property is shorthand for
                                                    setting both <code>align-items</code> and <code>justify-items</code>
                                                    at once.</p>

